name: Satanichia Kurumizawa McDowell (Gabriel Dropout)
description:
The perpetually unlucky demon girl from Gabriel Dropout. This model came out surprisingly flexible and should work rather well with most costumes, poses and other models.

Not trained on her clothing specifically to improve flexibility, you can fish for it using e.g. school uniform and related terms.
